verbose_text: Similar results were reported by Girgenrath et al. [XREF_BIBR] where the authors showed that (a) Fn14 is highly expressed on muscle progenitor cells; (b) recombinant TWEAK protein inhibits myogenic differentiation by preventing cell cycle arrest in myoblasts; and (c) TWEAK suppressed the expression of both myogenin and MyoD in differentiating myoblasts [XREF_BIBR].
